# Postiz daily-poster schedule (supercronic / standard 5-field cron).
# Times are in the container's TZ — set SCHEDULER_TZ in .env (default UTC).
# Edit the line below to change when the daily run fires, then:
#   make scheduler-restart
#
# min hour dom mon dow   command
30 14 * * *   /app/ops/scheduler/run-daily.sh >> /app/data/daily.log 2>&1
